Name: Add-NetSwitchTeamMember
Synopsis: Adds a network adapter member to an existing switch team.

Name: Get-NetSwitchTeamMember
Synopsis: Gets the current network adapter members of a switch team.

Name: Remove-NetSwitchTeamMember
Synopsis: Removes a network adapter member from a switch team.

Name: Rename-NetSwitchTeam
Synopsis: Changes the name of a switch team.
